name: starts-with
description: Returns `true` if the given string or array starts with prefix using strict equality for comparisons. Using fastest implementation from http://jsperf.com/starts-with-comparing-12-implementations

scripts.test-cov: npm run lint && node_modules/.bin/istanbul cover node_modules/.bin/_mocha -- --require should
scripts.test-travis: npm run lint && node_modules/.bin/istanbul cover node_modules/.bin/_mocha --report lcovonly -- --require should
scripts.coveralls: npm run test-travis && cat coverage/lcov.info | node_modules/.bin/coveralls
